\q1
\v 4 Blessed are they who live in your house;
\q1 They praise you continually. \qs (Instrumental break.)\qs*
\q1
\v 5 Blessed is the person who \add trusts you for their strength\add*—
\q1 who \add thinks about how to travel\add* to \add Mt.\add* Tsiyyon \add (Zion)\add*.
\q1
\v 6 Passing through the Valley of Tears, they find springs of water to drink.
