\q1
\v 11 because Yahweh God is our sun and shield.
\q1 Yahweh will give grace and glory.
\q1 He doesn’t withhold any good thing from those who walk in integrity.
\q1
\v 12 Army commander Yahweh,
\q1 blessed is the person who trusts in you.
\c 85
\s1 Prayer for national peace
