\q1
\v 11 Trustworthiness springs up from the ground,
\q1 and righteousness looks down from the sky.
\q1
\v 12 Yes, Yahweh will give his good blessings,
\q1 →and then our land will yield its crops.
\q1
\v 13 Righteousness will go before \add Yahweh\add*,
\q1 →and make a way for his footsteps.
